# Domain catalog for the active Reality path.
# Current routing policy:
#   - br0 TCP -> STEALTH_DOMAINS/VPN_STATIC_NETS -> REDIRECT :<lan-redirect-port> -> sing-box -> Reality
#   - br0 UDP/443 -> DROP for the same sets, forcing TCP fallback
#   - mobile clients -> router Reality ingress :<home-reality-port> -> sing-box -> Reality
# Channel A WireGuard is decommissioned; wgc1 remains only as cold-fallback NVRAM.

# Managed split checker. Keep this pinned so LAN/Wi-Fi and all home-first
# mobile channels report the same VPS egress for https://api.ipify.org.
ipset=/ipify.org/STEALTH_DOMAINS

